1
00:00:30,860 --> 00:00:33,340
♪Overcoming the boundary of confusion♪

2
00:00:33,500 --> 00:00:36,020
♪Holding onto my life
in the face of death threats♪

3
00:00:36,380 --> 00:00:39,300
♪I look into this dark night♪

4
00:00:41,220 --> 00:00:44,020
♪Never once has my soul
been extinguished♪

5
00:00:44,180 --> 00:00:46,820
♪With this passion♪

6
00:00:47,020 --> 00:00:50,940
♪My spirit is growing
to reach full swing♪

7
00:00:51,940 --> 00:00:54,780
♪Slashing the mountain
and the ocean apart♪

8
00:00:54,860 --> 00:00:57,180
♪Answering the true call on a sword♪

9
00:00:57,300 --> 00:01:01,140
♪I'm the chosen one
in this turbulent world♪

10
00:01:02,340 --> 00:01:05,260
♪Keep my distance from the world♪

11
00:01:05,540 --> 00:01:08,100
♪Who can understand my loneliness♪

12
00:01:08,220 --> 00:01:11,180
♪A single thought, looking down♪

13
00:01:11,820 --> 00:01:14,340
♪Blades unsheath,
frost flies everywhere♪

14
00:01:14,540 --> 00:01:17,100
♪A belief that cuts through the world♪

15
00:01:17,180 --> 00:01:21,100
♪Soaring towards the sky,
the sword reigns all♪

16
00:01:22,420 --> 00:01:24,900
♪Striding across the land
with a drunken gait♪

17
00:01:25,140 --> 00:01:27,700
♪I will protect the people
whenever I'm needed♪

18
00:01:27,860 --> 00:01:31,820
♪Atop the summit, you and I shall
battle for the world's best♪

19
00:01:31,820 --> 00:01:34,700
[Directed by Chen Zhoufei]

20
00:01:40,140 --> 00:01:42,320
[Dashing Youth]

21
00:01:42,320 --> 00:01:45,670
[Based on "Zhou Munan's
Juvenile Martial Arts Series"]

22
00:01:45,670 --> 00:01:49,020
[from fanqienovel.com and bkneng.com]

23
00:01:49,220 --> 00:01:52,020
[Episode 16]

24
00:01:57,900 --> 00:01:58,780
Your food is here, sir.

25
00:02:03,820 --> 00:02:04,580
Another round of drinks!

26
00:02:04,580 --> 00:02:05,620
Let me fill your cup!

27
00:02:06,220 --> 00:02:07,340
Waiter, get me a jar of liquor!

28
00:02:07,540 --> 00:02:08,100
Alright!

29
00:02:11,700 --> 00:02:13,260
Sir, let me fill your cup.

30
00:02:14,980 --> 00:02:16,140
Waiter, get us a pot of tea.

31
00:02:16,260 --> 00:02:18,100
Sir, sir.

32
00:02:18,540 --> 00:02:20,700
This table is reserved
only for important guests.

33
00:02:20,740 --> 00:02:21,900
Only important guests can sit here.

34
00:02:22,700 --> 00:02:23,420
Get me a cup of water.

35
00:02:39,180 --> 00:02:40,980
Here you go, sir.

36
00:02:54,900 --> 00:02:55,500
Sir.

37
00:02:57,060 --> 00:02:57,940
What would you like to drink?

38
00:02:59,300 --> 00:03:01,380
A jar of Sangluo, please.

39
00:03:01,620 --> 00:03:02,180
Sir,

40
00:03:02,700 --> 00:03:03,460
we have

41
00:03:03,620 --> 00:03:04,900
other premium liquor here.

42
00:03:05,980 --> 00:03:06,420
No need.

43
00:03:06,900 --> 00:03:07,980
The Sangluo will do.

44
00:03:08,820 --> 00:03:10,980
Liquor isn't meant for mere enjoyment

45
00:03:11,140 --> 00:03:12,180
and showing off.

46
00:03:12,780 --> 00:03:13,620
You have a point, sir.

47
00:03:26,580 --> 00:03:27,420
That table is taken.

48
00:03:29,340 --> 00:03:30,060
Young man,

49
00:03:30,380 --> 00:03:31,300
if you don't mind,

50
00:03:31,740 --> 00:03:32,660
why don't you join me?

51
00:03:38,220 --> 00:03:39,260
Is this place haunted?

52
00:03:40,060 --> 00:03:40,740
No one's sitting here.

53
00:03:41,180 --> 00:03:41,900
What I meant was,

54
00:03:42,060 --> 00:03:43,260
that this table has been reserved.

55
00:03:47,620 --> 00:03:48,900
Fine, then. Sorry for disturbing you.

56
00:03:54,780 --> 00:03:56,220
Sir, your liquor.

57
00:03:58,420 --> 00:03:59,460
Sangluo.

58
00:04:00,460 --> 00:04:01,940
Get another cup for this gentleman here.

59
00:04:04,380 --> 00:04:04,820
Alright.

60
00:04:05,860 --> 00:04:06,820
I have a friend

61
00:04:07,340 --> 00:04:08,220
who knows how to brew this.

62
00:04:11,100 --> 00:04:11,780
Try this, then.

63
00:04:20,660 --> 00:04:21,260
I think

64
00:04:23,780 --> 00:04:24,980
it's not as good as my friend's.

65
00:04:26,740 --> 00:04:27,660
Is your friend

66
00:04:27,660 --> 00:04:28,620
a brewmaster?

67
00:04:29,340 --> 00:04:30,740
He's just obsessed over liquor.

68
00:04:31,740 --> 00:04:33,260
May I have your name, young man?

69
00:04:34,580 --> 00:04:35,980
Sir, you're kind enough
to invite me to join you,

70
00:04:36,100 --> 00:04:37,020
so don't be so courteous.

71
00:04:39,660 --> 00:04:42,020
I have never had any parents.

72
00:04:42,340 --> 00:04:43,460
I come and leave

73
00:04:43,460 --> 00:04:44,140
empty-handed,

74
00:04:44,300 --> 00:04:45,420
so I gave myself the surname Sikong.

75
00:04:45,540 --> 00:04:46,700
I also desire to be like the wind

76
00:04:46,940 --> 00:04:47,740
that blows past and never returns.

77
00:04:48,100 --> 00:04:50,380
Therefore, my name is Sikong Changfeng.

78
00:04:52,980 --> 00:04:54,780
That's an interesting introduction.

79
00:04:55,540 --> 00:04:56,340
You must have thought long and hard.

80
00:04:59,020 --> 00:05:00,340
That's supposed to be a secret.

81
00:05:00,620 --> 00:05:01,700
You shouldn't have stated it clearly.

82
00:05:02,740 --> 00:05:03,140
Waiter,

83
00:05:03,940 --> 00:05:05,100
take this liquor away.

84
00:05:05,260 --> 00:05:05,700
We don't want it anymore.

85
00:05:06,140 --> 00:05:06,900
Get us something else.

86
00:05:08,140 --> 00:05:09,420
May I know

87
00:05:09,580 --> 00:05:11,220
what you'd like to order?

88
00:05:12,420 --> 00:05:14,180
I'd like some Qiulubai.

89
00:05:14,980 --> 00:05:15,780
Interesting.

90
00:05:17,100 --> 00:05:17,700
Sir,

91
00:05:18,300 --> 00:05:19,780
we're not serving Qiulubai today.

92
00:05:20,020 --> 00:05:20,620
Why?

93
00:05:21,100 --> 00:05:22,980
Qiulubai is only served
once every month

94
00:05:23,340 --> 00:05:24,980
and only four hours every time.

95
00:05:25,380 --> 00:05:26,940
Today isn't the right time.

96
00:05:28,940 --> 00:05:29,540
What about tomorrow?

97
00:05:29,780 --> 00:05:30,660
Not tomorrow.

98
00:05:30,740 --> 00:05:31,460
Not the day after

99
00:05:31,500 --> 00:05:32,580
or even the day after that.

100
00:05:32,820 --> 00:05:33,740
It's served
on the 14th day of the month,

101
00:05:33,780 --> 00:05:34,500
which is 13 days later.

102
00:05:34,860 --> 00:05:35,460
You'll have to wait.

103
00:05:36,420 --> 00:05:36,740
You...

104
00:05:37,340 --> 00:05:38,140
I'm curious,

105
00:05:38,500 --> 00:05:38,980
young man.

106
00:05:39,380 --> 00:05:40,660
Why do you want to order Qiulubai?

107
00:05:42,100 --> 00:05:42,940
To be honest,

108
00:05:43,460 --> 00:05:44,660
I came to Tianqi

109
00:05:44,940 --> 00:05:45,860
to meet a friend.

110
00:05:46,500 --> 00:05:47,740
The one that you mentioned?

111
00:05:47,980 --> 00:05:48,420
Yes.

112
00:05:48,860 --> 00:05:49,540
That friend of mine

113
00:05:49,820 --> 00:05:50,700
loves nothing else

114
00:05:50,980 --> 00:05:51,820
but liquor.

115
00:05:52,580 --> 00:05:53,180
Before we

116
00:05:53,340 --> 00:05:54,180
parted ways last time,

117
00:05:54,340 --> 00:05:55,060
he insisted

118
00:05:55,060 --> 00:05:56,580
that he wanted to drink
Qiulubai from Tianqi.

119
00:05:57,020 --> 00:05:57,620
That's why

120
00:05:57,860 --> 00:05:59,060
I wanted to buy a jar

121
00:05:59,220 --> 00:05:59,860
for him as a gift.

122
00:06:01,500 --> 00:06:03,860
Kid, you want Qiulubai?

123
00:06:04,300 --> 00:06:06,780
There's one up there.

124
00:06:08,980 --> 00:06:10,020
Is that Qiulubai?

125
00:06:10,700 --> 00:06:11,300
You talk too much.

126
00:06:15,460 --> 00:06:15,820
Waiter,

127
00:06:16,620 --> 00:06:17,820
how much does that jar of Qiulubai cost?

128
00:06:18,220 --> 00:06:18,700
Nothing.

129
00:06:19,540 --> 00:06:20,220
Nothing?

130
00:06:20,620 --> 00:06:21,660
As long as you can take it.

131
00:06:23,220 --> 00:06:23,820
That's simple.

132
00:06:23,940 --> 00:06:24,340
Changfeng.

133
00:06:27,940 --> 00:06:29,300
You want that Qiulubai?

134
00:06:29,860 --> 00:06:30,740
Since you stretched your hand out,

135
00:06:31,140 --> 00:06:32,500
that means you've
accepted the challenge.

136
00:06:36,500 --> 00:06:37,100
You set me up.

137
00:06:37,340 --> 00:06:38,500
Sir, how could you say that?

138
00:06:39,300 --> 00:06:40,140
That is indeed

139
00:06:40,140 --> 00:06:41,660
a 12-year-old Qiulubai,

140
00:06:41,860 --> 00:06:43,140
and the only one in this world.

141
00:06:43,660 --> 00:06:44,740
If you want it,

142
00:06:45,060 --> 00:06:46,340
you'll need
to rely on your capabilities.

143
00:06:46,820 --> 00:06:47,820
If you fail to do so,

144
00:06:49,340 --> 00:06:50,380
you need to leave something behind.

145
00:06:50,820 --> 00:06:52,660
As for what it will be...

146
00:06:52,740 --> 00:06:53,660
That's for me to decide.

147
00:06:56,700 --> 00:06:57,300
Master Xie.

148
00:06:58,270 --> 00:07:00,550
[Master Xie,
Brewmaster of Diaolou Tavern]

149
00:07:01,020 --> 00:07:01,580
Master Xie.

150
00:07:03,500 --> 00:07:04,060
Mr. Chen.

151
00:07:06,300 --> 00:07:07,740
Master Xie
is the strongest martial artist

152
00:07:08,020 --> 00:07:08,980
in Diaolou Tavern.

153
00:07:09,740 --> 00:07:10,780
Many men have tried

154
00:07:10,900 --> 00:07:11,860
to take the jar of liquor,

155
00:07:12,260 --> 00:07:13,580
but none has succeeded.

156
00:07:21,820 --> 00:07:22,660
That means

157
00:07:23,220 --> 00:07:24,220
that if I succeed,

158
00:07:24,780 --> 00:07:25,820
I'd be the first to do so.

159
00:07:27,900 --> 00:07:28,420
I guess so.

160
00:07:28,980 --> 00:07:29,740
Truly skilled martial artists

161
00:07:29,820 --> 00:07:30,780
would never take this liquor.

162
00:07:31,300 --> 00:07:32,340
Most of them who do so

163
00:07:32,580 --> 00:07:33,700
are people like you,

164
00:07:33,900 --> 00:07:35,500
still young and inexperienced.

165
00:07:36,860 --> 00:07:37,900
However, until now,

166
00:07:38,180 --> 00:07:39,140
the only person who has ever succeeded

167
00:07:39,460 --> 00:07:40,620
is Mr. Li.

168
00:07:41,860 --> 00:07:42,780
But he only did so

169
00:07:42,900 --> 00:07:44,180
just for fun

170
00:07:44,340 --> 00:07:45,900
and he left after touching the jar.

171
00:07:46,820 --> 00:07:47,420
So,

172
00:07:47,740 --> 00:07:48,780
if you manage to take it,

173
00:07:49,100 --> 00:07:50,260
you'd be the first to do so.

174
00:07:52,900 --> 00:07:53,260
Very well.

175
00:07:57,460 --> 00:07:58,100
Bring it on!

176
00:08:02,020 --> 00:08:02,660
Nice spear.

177
00:08:03,340 --> 00:08:04,140
The Silver-Moon Spear.

178
00:08:05,060 --> 00:08:05,660
I'll take that.

179
00:08:26,340 --> 00:08:27,260
He's overestimating himself.

180
00:08:29,420 --> 00:08:30,540
That's a nice spear,

181
00:08:31,660 --> 00:08:32,580
but what a waste.

182
00:08:33,100 --> 00:08:33,420
Go back!

183
00:08:37,500 --> 00:08:38,000
[Diaolou Tavern]

184
00:08:39,980 --> 00:08:40,820
I got wrecked as soon as I came.

185
00:08:41,380 --> 00:08:43,660
Tianqi City sure lives up to its name.

186
00:08:47,140 --> 00:08:47,900
Sikong Changfeng.

187
00:08:48,460 --> 00:08:49,300
It's been a while,

188
00:08:49,580 --> 00:08:50,380
but you didn't have
to welcome me like this.

189
00:08:51,060 --> 00:08:51,780
Baili Dongjun?

190
00:08:53,340 --> 00:08:55,020
Not bad, you still remember me.

191
00:08:55,500 --> 00:08:56,420
When did you arrive?

192
00:08:56,620 --> 00:08:57,460
Why didn't you come to visit me?

193
00:08:57,660 --> 00:08:58,580
I just got here today

194
00:08:58,780 --> 00:08:59,740
and I was about to visit you.

195
00:08:59,980 --> 00:09:02,420
Long time no see, Sikong Changfeng.

196
00:09:04,460 --> 00:09:05,140
Mr. Zhuomo.

197
00:09:06,540 --> 00:09:07,260
Anyway,

198
00:09:07,900 --> 00:09:09,380
you got into a fight
as soon as you arrived here

199
00:09:09,940 --> 00:09:10,780
and you got hit hard?

200
00:09:11,500 --> 00:09:12,380
Don't even mention it.

201
00:09:12,900 --> 00:09:13,340
I thought

202
00:09:13,340 --> 00:09:14,420
I should prepare a gift

203
00:09:14,620 --> 00:09:15,460
to celebrate our reunion.

204
00:09:15,980 --> 00:09:16,540
Normal liquor

205
00:09:16,540 --> 00:09:17,460
pales in comparison to yours.

206
00:09:17,700 --> 00:09:18,780
But they've sold out their best liquor,

207
00:09:19,100 --> 00:09:19,820
so I had to fight for it.

208
00:09:20,460 --> 00:09:21,220
But in the end,

209
00:09:21,220 --> 00:09:21,820
I lost the fight,

210
00:09:22,060 --> 00:09:22,780
the liquor,

211
00:09:22,980 --> 00:09:24,100
and even my spear.

212
00:09:25,580 --> 00:09:26,780
You couldn't defeat him?

213
00:09:27,180 --> 00:09:29,540
What about the two of us?

214
00:09:35,660 --> 00:09:36,700
Master Xie, your Jingang Force Field

215
00:09:36,900 --> 00:09:37,740
has improved a lot.

216
00:09:39,100 --> 00:09:39,900
Unfortunately,

217
00:09:41,420 --> 00:09:43,100
that young man managed to break it.

218
00:09:46,420 --> 00:09:47,540
He's got potential.

219
00:09:48,420 --> 00:09:49,180
Indeed,

220
00:09:49,980 --> 00:09:51,060
he's like an eagle.

221
00:09:55,860 --> 00:09:56,220
Look.

222
00:09:57,900 --> 00:09:58,460
This way, please.

223
00:10:05,380 --> 00:10:06,860
You've already got some helpers?

224
00:10:08,540 --> 00:10:09,700
Is that jar over there

225
00:10:10,020 --> 00:10:10,820
the Qiulubai?

226
00:10:11,580 --> 00:10:11,860
Yes,

227
00:10:12,900 --> 00:10:13,780
it's a 12-year-old

228
00:10:13,780 --> 00:10:14,300
Qiulubai.

229
00:10:15,340 --> 00:10:15,860
I want it.

230
00:10:26,460 --> 00:10:27,660
That's a strong palm move.

231
00:10:28,740 --> 00:10:29,860
I see, I'm not the only brewer

232
00:10:30,140 --> 00:10:31,500
who knows martial arts.

233
00:10:32,220 --> 00:10:33,500
Dongjun, don't be rude.

234
00:10:33,980 --> 00:10:34,780
This is

235
00:10:34,780 --> 00:10:36,380
the top-ranked brewmaster
in Diaolou Tavern.

236
00:10:37,140 --> 00:10:38,020
Everyone in Tianqi

237
00:10:38,020 --> 00:10:39,100
addresses him

238
00:10:39,100 --> 00:10:39,980
as Master Xie.

239
00:10:41,380 --> 00:10:42,060
Mr. Zhuomo.

240
00:10:42,140 --> 00:10:43,260
Master Xie, sorry for offending you.

241
00:10:44,100 --> 00:10:44,540
This is

242
00:10:44,540 --> 00:10:45,780
my new junior.

243
00:10:46,580 --> 00:10:48,300
I apologize for his rude behavior.

244
00:10:49,420 --> 00:10:50,940
This is Mr. Li's new disciple?

245
00:10:51,340 --> 00:10:51,860
No wonder.

246
00:10:52,820 --> 00:10:53,940
Did you fight me

247
00:10:54,940 --> 00:10:55,780
for the liquor?

248
00:10:58,460 --> 00:10:59,660
That's my friend's spear.

249
00:11:03,660 --> 00:11:05,100
Your friend failed the challenge.

250
00:11:05,340 --> 00:11:06,460
He has to leave something behind.

251
00:11:07,180 --> 00:11:08,020
That's the rule.

252
00:11:08,100 --> 00:11:09,060
But if I win,

253
00:11:09,660 --> 00:11:10,660
can I take both the spear

254
00:11:10,660 --> 00:11:11,340
and the liquor?

255
00:11:11,860 --> 00:11:12,620
Of course.

256
00:11:14,060 --> 00:11:14,380
Come on!

257
00:11:15,740 --> 00:11:16,820
A fighting challenge for a jar of liquor

258
00:11:17,140 --> 00:11:18,060
seems pretty weird.

259
00:11:18,460 --> 00:11:19,420
How about I challenge you
to something else?

260
00:11:23,100 --> 00:11:23,700
What do you have in mind?

261
00:11:24,860 --> 00:11:25,740
Let's see who can

262
00:11:26,020 --> 00:11:26,940
make the best liquor.

263
00:11:28,100 --> 00:11:28,740
What?

264
00:11:29,060 --> 00:11:29,980
This guy is crazy!

265
00:11:30,260 --> 00:11:31,620
He's challenging Master Xie
to a brewing showdown?

266
00:11:31,940 --> 00:11:32,820
He's too full of himself.

267
00:11:33,900 --> 00:11:35,020
Let's meet again
on the 14th day of the month.

268
00:11:35,460 --> 00:11:37,260
By then, I will bring my own liquor

269
00:11:37,260 --> 00:11:38,020
to Diaolou Tavern.

270
00:11:38,460 --> 00:11:39,260
Prepare the best liquor you have

271
00:11:39,300 --> 00:11:40,500
in Diaolou Tavern

272
00:11:40,900 --> 00:11:41,620
and the best liquor taster

273
00:11:41,620 --> 00:11:42,780
in the city.

274
00:11:43,140 --> 00:11:45,100
Then, I'll be taking that spear

275
00:11:45,460 --> 00:11:46,380
and the jar of liquor.

276
00:11:46,940 --> 00:11:47,980
You insolent boy.

277
00:11:48,580 --> 00:11:49,860
Do you know what you're saying?

278
00:11:50,580 --> 00:11:51,260
Even if you are

279
00:11:51,260 --> 00:11:52,460
Mr. Li's last disciple,

280
00:11:52,740 --> 00:11:54,380
you should keep your ego in check.

281
00:11:58,180 --> 00:11:58,580
Master Xie,

282
00:11:58,940 --> 00:12:00,700
my junior has been mastering

283
00:12:00,940 --> 00:12:03,220
the art of making liquor
for over a decade.

284
00:12:03,300 --> 00:12:04,540
And I have been making liquor
for over 40 years.

285
00:12:05,140 --> 00:12:05,620
Fine.

286
00:12:08,420 --> 00:12:10,100
A good jar of liquor
can tell hundreds of stories.

287
00:12:10,220 --> 00:12:11,820
The passion of youth,
the composure of a middle-aged man,

288
00:12:11,820 --> 00:12:13,140
and the richness that comes with age,
they're all different.

289
00:12:13,340 --> 00:12:14,620
Having more years
of experience under your belt

290
00:12:14,980 --> 00:12:16,140
doesn't mean you can defeat me.

291
00:12:25,340 --> 00:12:26,660
I'll be waiting, then.

292
00:12:32,820 --> 00:12:33,700
What brings you here?

293
00:12:34,060 --> 00:12:34,620
I was

294
00:12:34,860 --> 00:12:36,220
planning to take my junior

295
00:12:36,340 --> 00:12:37,900
to somewhere fun,

296
00:12:38,060 --> 00:12:38,420
but when

297
00:12:38,420 --> 00:12:39,580
we passed by Diaolou Tavern,

298
00:12:39,940 --> 00:12:40,900
we heard a commotion.

299
00:12:41,140 --> 00:12:41,620
So

300
00:12:41,620 --> 00:12:43,100
we decided to check it out.

301
00:12:43,180 --> 00:12:44,180
Well, it's just me

302
00:12:44,180 --> 00:12:44,940
who wanted to check it out.

303
00:12:44,940 --> 00:12:45,780
And it just so happened

304
00:12:45,780 --> 00:12:47,180
that you were kicked out.

305
00:12:47,180 --> 00:12:48,780
I was still wondering

306
00:12:48,780 --> 00:12:49,460
how I should respond

307
00:12:49,460 --> 00:12:50,020
when he

308
00:12:50,020 --> 00:12:50,420
recognized you

309
00:12:50,420 --> 00:12:51,460
from afar.

310
00:12:51,460 --> 00:12:51,900
He

311
00:12:51,980 --> 00:12:53,100
flew towards you

312
00:12:53,180 --> 00:12:54,780
and saved you from falling.

313
00:12:56,780 --> 00:12:58,260
So you've really
become Mr. Li's disciple?

314
00:12:58,540 --> 00:12:59,420
That means you're Mr. Zhuomo,

315
00:12:59,740 --> 00:13:00,140
I mean,

316
00:13:00,140 --> 00:13:01,180
your second senior's junior.

317
00:13:01,460 --> 00:13:01,900
How nice.

318
00:13:02,660 --> 00:13:03,420
You're doing great yourself.

319
00:13:03,820 --> 00:13:04,380
You got here alive

320
00:13:04,700 --> 00:13:05,780
to meet me.

321
00:13:08,260 --> 00:13:08,820
Second Senior,

322
00:13:09,220 --> 00:13:10,220
where are you going exactly?

323
00:13:12,700 --> 00:13:15,380
Well, we're here.

324
00:13:15,380 --> 00:13:20,600
[Baihua Hall]

325
00:13:44,980 --> 00:13:45,540
Come in.

326
00:13:45,620 --> 00:13:46,420
Let's get you a private room.

327
00:13:46,660 --> 00:13:47,340
Nice.

328
00:13:47,340 --> 00:13:48,660
I'll leave you a good tip.

329
00:13:49,900 --> 00:13:50,380
Sir.

330
00:13:50,620 --> 00:13:51,180
You're here.

331
00:13:51,460 --> 00:13:52,100
Come on.

332
00:14:00,420 --> 00:14:02,540
