333
00:14:02,820 --> 00:14:04,220
Not at all.

334
00:14:05,100 --> 00:14:06,580
This is Baihua Hall.

335
00:14:07,020 --> 00:14:07,740
It's different.

336
00:14:09,060 --> 00:14:10,140
How is it different?

337
00:14:10,860 --> 00:14:11,820
Because of her.

338
00:14:12,780 --> 00:14:13,780
She makes this place different.

339
00:14:14,780 --> 00:14:17,020
Years ago, Gu Jianmen and I

340
00:14:17,460 --> 00:14:18,740
came here for the first time.

341
00:14:18,900 --> 00:14:20,340
She was playing the guqin.

342
00:14:21,260 --> 00:14:22,660
Gu Jianmen probably was drunk

343
00:14:23,220 --> 00:14:24,780
and when he heard her playing,

344
00:14:24,980 --> 00:14:26,060
he got into the mood

345
00:14:27,140 --> 00:14:28,740
and danced with his sword.

346
00:14:36,340 --> 00:14:38,620
It was a magnificent scene to behold.

347
00:14:46,940 --> 00:14:47,900
So handsome.

348
00:14:48,620 --> 00:14:49,540
His sword

349
00:14:49,540 --> 00:14:51,060
gathered a flurry of petals

350
00:14:51,180 --> 00:14:53,140
in a sparkling array of colors.

351
00:15:28,380 --> 00:15:29,700
The petals eventually formed

352
00:15:29,700 --> 00:15:31,740
into a flowery bridge

353
00:15:32,020 --> 00:15:32,820
