354
00:15:33,060 --> 00:15:35,300
her pavilion up there.

355
00:15:41,380 --> 00:15:42,220
Gu Jianmen said

356
00:15:42,860 --> 00:15:44,460
that her music speaks
volumes about herself.

357
00:15:44,900 --> 00:15:45,980
He felt that the lady

358
00:15:45,980 --> 00:15:47,340
was his destined lover.

359
00:15:48,300 --> 00:15:49,700
So he stepped onto the petal bridge

360
00:15:50,260 --> 00:15:52,580
and walked towards the pavilion,

361
00:15:53,380 --> 00:15:56,460
then lifted one veil
after another to see her.

362
00:15:56,620 --> 00:15:57,980
Be careful, sir!

363
00:16:31,500 --> 00:16:31,980
And then?

364
00:16:34,140 --> 00:16:35,540
And then, Gu Jianmen came down.

365
00:16:36,060 --> 00:16:36,940
He got rejected.

366
00:16:40,460 --> 00:16:41,740
That was

367
00:16:41,740 --> 00:16:43,140
quite some years ago.

368
00:16:43,300 --> 00:16:44,420
I'm sure the young lady

369
00:16:44,500 --> 00:16:45,580
has blossomed

370
00:16:45,580 --> 00:16:46,780
into a fine and mature woman.

371
00:16:47,580 --> 00:16:48,540
Everyone in Tianqi

372
00:16:48,540 --> 00:16:49,540
knows her name.

373
00:16:49,860 --> 00:16:51,620
I wonder if Gu Jianmen

374
00:16:51,900 --> 00:16:53,420
