375
00:16:54,780 --> 00:16:57,900
Mr. Lei, it's been so long
since you last came.

376
00:16:58,900 --> 00:16:59,700
Not as long

377
00:16:59,700 --> 00:17:00,740
as Gu did.

378
00:17:02,700 --> 00:17:04,100
How long exactly do you mean?

379
00:17:04,780 --> 00:17:06,380
Not that long ago, actually.

380
00:17:15,980 --> 00:17:17,100
I can feel a murderous aura.

381
00:17:25,340 --> 00:17:26,620
Miss... Miss Li.

382
00:17:27,260 --> 00:17:29,020
Picking up such bad habits
at such a young age.

383
00:17:29,180 --> 00:17:29,500
I...

384
00:17:29,860 --> 00:17:31,060
I'm innocent.

385
00:17:33,780 --> 00:17:34,420
Xinyue.

386
00:17:36,180 --> 00:17:36,780
Yes.

387
00:17:37,540 --> 00:17:38,380
Baili Dongjun,

388
00:17:38,420 --> 00:17:40,060
you're picking up such bad habits
at your age.

389
00:17:40,140 --> 00:17:41,500
I told you not to come here,

390
00:17:41,500 --> 00:17:42,220
but you insisted.

391
00:17:42,220 --> 00:17:43,420
I said I didn't want to come,

392
00:17:43,420 --> 00:17:44,220
but you still

393
00:17:44,260 --> 00:17:45,820
dragged me in here anyway.

394
00:17:45,940 --> 00:17:46,300
Well?

395
00:17:46,380 --> 00:17:47,140
Are you satisfied?

396
00:17:47,420 --> 00:17:48,020
Happy now?

397
00:17:48,340 --> 00:17:49,700
This isn't the place

398
00:17:49,740 --> 00:17:51,140
for me to come.

399
00:17:53,380 --> 00:17:54,420
Do you have no shame?

400
00:17:54,500 --> 00:17:54,900
Shut up.

401
00:17:57,460 --> 00:17:57,860
Xinyue.

402
00:17:59,300 --> 00:18:00,020
Let's go home,

403
00:18:00,820 --> 00:18:01,980
back to our cozy little home.

404
00:18:02,300 --> 00:18:03,220
When do you plan

405
00:18:03,220 --> 00:18:04,660
to come here again?

406
00:18:04,700 --> 00:18:05,220
Not anymore.

407
00:18:05,380 --> 00:18:06,740
I'll never come here again.

408
00:18:06,780 --> 00:18:08,260
Even if my junior invites me,

409
00:18:08,260 --> 00:18:09,220
I'd never come again.

410
00:18:11,300 --> 00:18:11,580
Come on.

411
00:18:14,140 --> 00:18:14,700
Dongjun,

412
00:18:15,380 --> 00:18:16,740
have fun while you're young.

413
00:18:16,900 --> 00:18:17,580
Your good days

414
00:18:18,700 --> 00:18:19,260
are numbered.

415
00:18:19,780 --> 00:18:20,140
Dongjun.

416
00:18:20,180 --> 00:18:20,500
Come on.

417
00:18:20,540 --> 00:18:20,940
Dongjun.

418
00:18:22,460 --> 00:18:23,100
Come on.

419
00:18:23,340 --> 00:18:24,780
Xinyue!

420
00:18:25,020 --> 00:18:26,020
I was wrong!

421
00:18:30,060 --> 00:18:31,260
Where are we?

422
00:18:32,380 --> 00:18:33,540
What should we do?

423
00:18:35,540 --> 00:18:37,180
Gentlemen.

424
00:18:37,860 --> 00:18:39,020
What... What is it?

425
00:18:39,820 --> 00:18:42,260
What handsome young men we have here.

426
00:18:42,300 --> 00:18:43,260
Madam Ziyi.

427
00:18:44,060 --> 00:18:45,180
Is Miss Feng

428
00:18:45,340 --> 00:18:46,420
still playing tonight?

429
00:18:46,700 --> 00:18:48,380
I'm getting impatient.

430
00:18:49,460 --> 00:18:50,500
Don't be.

431
00:18:54,660 --> 00:18:55,780
She's here.

432
00:18:57,900 --> 00:18:58,980
Alright.

433
00:19:01,940 --> 00:19:02,900
Second Master Tu.

434
00:19:04,100 --> 00:19:05,780
You're here just in time.

435
00:19:05,780 --> 00:19:06,860
This melody

436
00:19:08,660 --> 00:19:09,860
has a melancholy vibe to it.

437
00:19:12,380 --> 00:19:14,500
I've heard this before.

438
00:19:15,260 --> 00:19:15,860
Have you been here?

439
00:19:16,540 --> 00:19:17,300
No.

440
00:19:17,300 --> 00:19:18,780
Do you know music?

441
00:19:19,460 --> 00:19:20,260
No.

442
00:19:21,140 --> 00:19:21,980
I've heard this score before.

443
00:19:22,700 --> 00:19:23,460
It's called The Jiangnan Moon.

444
00:19:25,540 --> 00:19:26,780
"All is home
as the midnight gong chimes,

445
00:19:27,340 --> 00:19:28,580
only the rustling of leaves
is heard at such times.

446
00:19:29,380 --> 00:19:30,740
A white glow illuminates
the autumn night,

447
00:19:32,340 --> 00:19:33,460
in my hometown the moon shines bright."

448
00:19:36,700 --> 00:19:38,100
This score is about one's
longing for home.

449
00:21:09,820 --> 00:21:10,740
Sir.

450
00:21:11,740 --> 00:21:12,340
Miss.

451
00:21:13,660 --> 00:21:15,020
That's not a title I deserve to hold.

452
00:21:15,220 --> 00:21:16,260
Our young lady would like to meet you.

453
00:21:17,580 --> 00:21:20,100
Your young lady is?

454
00:21:20,980 --> 00:21:21,780
Young man,

455
00:21:22,100 --> 00:21:23,500
are you really that ignorant?

456
00:21:23,740 --> 00:21:24,500
There's only

457
00:21:24,500 --> 00:21:26,060
one young lady

458
00:21:26,180 --> 00:21:27,100
in Baihua Hall.

459
00:21:27,500 --> 00:21:28,220
Wait, wait.

460
00:21:29,250 --> 00:21:30,490
Who is

461
00:21:30,500 --> 00:21:31,100
this dumb kid?

462
00:21:31,500 --> 00:21:33,180
Why is Miss Feng inviting only him?

463
00:21:33,700 --> 00:21:35,500
I come here every day

464
00:21:35,820 --> 00:21:36,540
and I've spent quite a lot...

465
00:21:36,540 --> 00:21:37,060
Second Master Tu.

466
00:21:37,060 --> 00:21:38,260
I still haven't met Miss Feng in person.

467
00:21:38,300 --> 00:21:39,340
How come he gets to meet her

468
00:21:39,340 --> 00:21:40,660
on his first visit?

469
00:21:41,060 --> 00:21:42,100
Second Master Tu,

470
00:21:42,420 --> 00:21:43,940
calm down, please.

471
00:21:44,420 --> 00:21:45,500
Aren't you from Qianjin House?

472
00:21:45,500 --> 00:21:47,060
What does that have to do with this?

473
00:21:47,060 --> 00:21:48,220
Forget about Qianjin House tonight.

474
00:21:48,460 --> 00:21:49,260
We're all here

475
00:21:49,260 --> 00:21:50,300
for the music.

476
00:21:50,660 --> 00:21:51,100
Everyone.

477
00:21:52,180 --> 00:21:54,020
Baihua Hall is treating us unfairly.

478
00:21:54,260 --> 00:21:55,300
Don't you think so?

479
00:21:55,500 --> 00:21:56,500
- Yeah!
- Yeah!

480
00:21:57,260 --> 00:21:58,100
Yeah!

481
00:21:58,300 --> 00:21:58,900
Why him?

482
00:21:59,980 --> 00:22:01,180
Please, gentlemen.

483
00:22:01,500 --> 00:22:03,100
Yes, it's inappropriate.

484
00:22:03,340 --> 00:22:04,180
I guess I'm not going.

485
00:22:05,060 --> 00:22:06,660
Do you know who you're rejecting?

486
00:22:07,940 --> 00:22:09,580
Wait, don't be angry, miss.

487
00:22:10,260 --> 00:22:11,060
That's enough.

488
00:22:12,900 --> 00:22:13,700
It's not easy to meet someone
who resonates with you.

489
00:22:14,020 --> 00:22:14,580
Who knows,

490
00:22:14,740 --> 00:22:15,700
she might be from your hometown.

491
00:22:15,700 --> 00:22:16,500
Calm down, Second Master Tu.

492
00:22:16,660 --> 00:22:17,020
Calm down.

493
00:22:27,980 --> 00:22:29,100
Calm down, everyone.

494
00:22:29,300 --> 00:22:30,500
Let me get some fine liquor
for all of you.

495
00:22:30,500 --> 00:22:31,500
He's going up just like that?

496
00:22:31,700 --> 00:22:32,940
Isn't anyone going to stop him?

497
00:22:33,060 --> 00:22:33,740
Don't you go there!

498
00:22:33,740 --> 00:22:34,820
Let's see who dares challenge me.

499
00:22:35,500 --> 00:22:36,980
Fine, fine.

500
00:22:40,740 --> 00:22:41,100
Dumbo!

501
00:22:41,740 --> 00:22:42,100
You piece of junk!

502
00:22:45,340 --> 00:22:45,980
Go ahead.

503
00:22:52,060 --> 00:22:52,660
I...

504
00:22:53,740 --> 00:22:54,940
Calm down, Second Master Tu.

505
00:22:59,980 --> 00:23:00,740
Young man.

506
00:23:01,020 --> 00:23:02,740
Madam.

507
00:23:03,660 --> 00:23:05,540
Can you get me a table

508
00:23:05,780 --> 00:23:07,180
so I could wait for him?

509
00:23:07,660 --> 00:23:08,460
Sir,

510
00:23:08,740 --> 00:23:10,420
are you sure he'll be back

511
00:23:10,500 --> 00:23:11,500
by tonight?

512
00:23:12,700 --> 00:23:14,180
The night is young

513
00:23:14,260 --> 00:23:15,300
and he's got a lady in his arms.

514
00:23:15,580 --> 00:23:17,020
Who knows how long they'd take?

515
00:23:17,580 --> 00:23:18,180
Why don't I

516
00:23:18,420 --> 00:23:19,740
get you another girl

517
00:23:19,740 --> 00:23:21,340
to keep you company?

518
00:23:21,420 --> 00:23:22,340
No need.

519
00:23:22,580 --> 00:23:23,220
That's not necessary.

520
00:23:25,260 --> 00:23:26,020
Sikong Changfeng,

521
00:23:26,940 --> 00:23:28,740
I won't be waiting for you tonight.

522
00:23:29,420 --> 00:23:31,740
Enjoy.

523
00:23:34,500 --> 00:23:35,700
Come again!

524
00:23:36,940 --> 00:23:37,500
Come on.

525
00:23:45,740 --> 00:23:46,260
Thank you.

526
00:23:55,300 --> 00:23:56,020
Is it you?

527
00:23:57,020 --> 00:23:57,780
Greetings, miss.

528
00:23:58,260 --> 00:23:59,020
My name is Sikong Changfeng.

529
00:24:00,100 --> 00:24:01,260
Are you from the Wei City?

530
00:24:03,020 --> 00:24:03,740
The Wei City?

531
00:24:04,820 --> 00:24:06,020
Where do you come from?

532
00:24:06,740 --> 00:24:07,460
I don't remember.

533
00:24:07,940 --> 00:24:09,300
Then, where did you learn

534
00:24:09,820 --> 00:24:10,940
to play that score?

535
00:24:11,700 --> 00:24:12,740
I don't remember that as well.

536
00:24:14,340 --> 00:24:15,900
Why can't you remember anything?

537
00:24:16,420 --> 00:24:17,660
Are you just plain forgetful,

538
00:24:17,700 --> 00:24:18,780
or is there something wrong
with your brain?

539
00:24:19,500 --> 00:24:20,500
Don't be mad, miss.

540
00:24:21,740 --> 00:24:22,420
I really can't

541
00:24:22,420 --> 00:24:23,460
remember my past.

542
00:24:24,340 --> 00:24:25,540
I have been wandering
around Jiangnan since young.

543
00:24:25,940 --> 00:24:27,260
Perhaps it was

544
00:24:27,260 --> 00:24:28,260
a traveler

545
00:24:28,260 --> 00:24:29,020
who taught me the score.

546
00:24:29,420 --> 00:24:30,820
When I heard you playing it,

547
00:24:31,220 --> 00:24:32,900
I couldn't help but accompany.

548
00:24:33,900 --> 00:24:35,020
I hope you won't blame me for it.

549
00:24:36,020 --> 00:24:37,540
I didn't mean to blame you.

550
00:24:38,500 --> 00:24:39,580
It was me who lost my composure.

551
00:24:41,540 --> 00:24:42,780
I had a big brother

552
00:24:43,500 --> 00:24:44,900
