553
00:24:46,340 --> 00:24:48,020
I mistook you for him.

554
00:24:49,220 --> 00:24:49,940
Looks like

555
00:24:51,500 --> 00:24:52,660
I overthought it.

556
00:24:53,380 --> 00:24:54,140
You may leave now.

557
00:24:55,180 --> 00:24:56,100
Don't tell anyone

558
00:24:57,180 --> 00:24:58,740
about my brother

559
00:24:58,980 --> 00:24:59,900
or how I lost my composure.

560
00:25:00,060 --> 00:25:00,980
Don't tell anyone else

561
00:25:01,660 --> 00:25:02,260
and ruin

562
00:25:02,260 --> 00:25:03,460
my reputation out there.

563
00:25:03,740 --> 00:25:05,540
Well, miss?

564
00:25:05,780 --> 00:25:07,020
Why do you keep calling me?

565
00:25:08,940 --> 00:25:09,860
Actually,

566
00:25:11,780 --> 00:25:13,100
I'd love to have a little sister.

567
00:25:14,220 --> 00:25:15,740
How impudent of you.

568
00:25:15,980 --> 00:25:16,540
Someone,

569
00:25:16,780 --> 00:25:17,460
get this shameless man

570
00:25:17,460 --> 00:25:18,220
out of here.

571
00:25:18,540 --> 00:25:19,060
Wait, wait.

572
00:25:19,420 --> 00:25:19,860
Miss,

573
00:25:20,540 --> 00:25:21,420
hear me out.

574
00:25:21,860 --> 00:25:22,900
That's not what I meant.

575
00:25:23,620 --> 00:25:24,740
I've been a vagrant my whole life

576
00:25:25,260 --> 00:25:26,220
and I've never been envious

577
00:25:26,220 --> 00:25:26,900
of people who have parents,

578
00:25:27,340 --> 00:25:28,220
but I've always wanted

579
00:25:28,740 --> 00:25:29,620
to have a little sister.

580
00:25:30,340 --> 00:25:31,220
Having a little sister feels like

581
00:25:31,820 --> 00:25:33,460
having someone to protect.

582
00:25:35,220 --> 00:25:35,980
That's why...

583
00:25:39,100 --> 00:25:40,220
That's why I think

584
00:25:40,900 --> 00:25:41,500
that if I had

585
00:25:41,500 --> 00:25:42,500
a sister to protect,

586
00:25:43,180 --> 00:25:44,180
that would be something

587
00:25:44,460 --> 00:25:45,700
that I can take pride in.

588
00:25:50,580 --> 00:25:51,180
I won't be your sister.

589
00:25:51,620 --> 00:25:52,180
Why?

590
00:25:55,540 --> 00:25:55,980
Miss,

591
00:25:57,060 --> 00:25:59,220
what's your brother's name?

592
00:25:59,940 --> 00:26:00,620
Wei Luoli.

593
00:26:00,980 --> 00:26:02,980
Alright, from now on,

594
00:26:03,460 --> 00:26:04,340
my name will be Wei Luoli.

595
00:26:15,140 --> 00:26:15,940
You...

596
00:26:16,500 --> 00:26:18,220
How dare you tease me time and again?

597
00:26:20,200 --> 00:26:23,920
[Feng Qiuyu,
Top Courtesan of Baihua Hall]

598
00:26:31,260 --> 00:26:32,940
You didn't kick me that hard.

599
00:26:33,660 --> 00:26:34,340
That means

600
00:26:35,540 --> 00:26:36,500
you weren't really angry.

601
00:26:39,060 --> 00:26:39,460
Miss,

602
00:26:40,060 --> 00:26:40,740
I may have forgotten

603
00:26:40,740 --> 00:26:41,980
whether I'm from Wei or not,

604
00:26:42,260 --> 00:26:44,020
but we're both from Jiangnan.

605
00:26:44,660 --> 00:26:45,780
And we know the same score.

606
00:26:46,340 --> 00:26:46,940
This shows

607
00:26:47,460 --> 00:26:49,460
that we have an affinity.

608
00:26:51,060 --> 00:26:51,940
Just now, I said

609
00:26:52,460 --> 00:26:53,100
that I wanted

610
00:26:53,100 --> 00:26:54,140
a sister like you

611
00:26:55,060 --> 00:26:55,780
and I mean it.

612
00:26:59,380 --> 00:26:59,820
Yes,

613
00:27:00,300 --> 00:27:01,420
this is our first time meeting.

614
00:27:01,780 --> 00:27:02,580
Getting a brother

615
00:27:02,740 --> 00:27:03,780
all of a sudden for no reason

616
00:27:04,220 --> 00:27:05,820
must be confusing for you.

617
00:27:07,220 --> 00:27:08,100
I have crossed the line.

618
00:27:10,860 --> 00:27:12,060
I'm not from Jiangnan.

619
00:27:12,700 --> 00:27:13,820
I'm from...

620
00:27:16,100 --> 00:27:17,100
You're trying to trick me again.

621
00:27:18,260 --> 00:27:19,300
No, miss.

622
00:27:19,660 --> 00:27:20,660
I have a friend who said

623
00:27:21,260 --> 00:27:23,020
that words could be deceiving,

624
00:27:23,340 --> 00:27:24,180
but music couldn't.

625
00:27:25,060 --> 00:27:26,420
That's because music is the purest

626
00:27:27,540 --> 00:27:29,420
and cleanest thing in the whole world.

627
00:27:30,100 --> 00:27:30,820
So, miss,

628
00:27:31,380 --> 00:27:32,500
no matter where you're from,

629
00:27:33,220 --> 00:27:35,140
what you miss most is Jiangnan.

630
00:27:35,580 --> 00:27:37,620
The person you care about the most
is also there.

631
00:27:38,420 --> 00:27:40,620
What is your friend's name?

632
00:27:45,300 --> 00:27:46,020
Baili Dongjun.

633
00:27:51,220 --> 00:27:52,380
That's a fine name.

634
00:27:53,900 --> 00:27:54,620
I'm tired.

635
00:27:55,420 --> 00:27:56,860
Let's end this conversation for now.

636
00:27:57,540 --> 00:27:58,180
Linglong.

637
00:27:59,140 --> 00:27:59,820
See our guest off.

638
00:28:02,060 --> 00:28:02,540
Miss.

639
00:28:04,100 --> 00:28:05,140
You may meet many people
throughout your life,

640
00:28:05,580 --> 00:28:06,500
but only befriend a few.

641
00:28:07,620 --> 00:28:08,940
I believe that true friends do exist.

642
00:28:09,660 --> 00:28:11,100
Your guqin and my leaf

643
00:28:11,820 --> 00:28:12,780
resonated together.

644
00:28:14,420 --> 00:28:15,060
I will be back.

645
00:28:21,180 --> 00:28:22,260
Now you sound

646
00:28:22,540 --> 00:28:23,820
like a scholar.

647
00:28:37,780 --> 00:28:38,500
If you ask me,

648
00:28:39,340 --> 00:28:40,260
I'm just a vagabond.

649
00:28:55,100 --> 00:28:55,580
Miss,

650
00:28:56,100 --> 00:28:57,780
you seem to fancy...

651
00:28:58,220 --> 00:28:59,820
No, I mean, you don't hate him.

652
00:29:04,060 --> 00:29:05,180
He's interesting,

653
00:29:06,340 --> 00:29:06,940
isn't he?

654
00:29:22,340 --> 00:29:23,700
Luoxia, you frightened me.

655
00:29:26,100 --> 00:29:27,020
What brings you here?

656
00:29:27,780 --> 00:29:28,940
I've been practicing the whole day

657
00:29:28,940 --> 00:29:30,180
under my master's watchful eye.

658
00:29:30,460 --> 00:29:31,940
I thought we could
grab a drink together,

659
00:29:32,460 --> 00:29:33,300
but you weren't here.

660
00:29:33,540 --> 00:29:34,420
What a letdown.

661
00:29:46,100 --> 00:29:46,620
You...

662
00:29:48,020 --> 00:29:48,940
Did you go to a brothel?

663
00:29:51,180 --> 00:29:52,020
It's not what you think.

664
00:29:58,460 --> 00:29:59,380
I knew it.

665
00:29:59,740 --> 00:30:00,820
I can smell the scent of rouge.

666
00:30:00,820 --> 00:30:02,060
Even the night breeze
couldn't blow it off you.

667
00:30:02,300 --> 00:30:03,300
You did visit a brothel.

668
00:30:03,500 --> 00:30:04,420
That's not a brothel.

669
00:30:04,460 --> 00:30:05,420
It's Baihua Hall,

670
00:30:05,500 --> 00:30:06,300
a place for music.

671
00:30:06,660 --> 00:30:08,020
I heard

672
00:30:08,420 --> 00:30:09,060
that you

673
00:30:09,100 --> 00:30:10,100
had a girl that you fancied,

674
00:30:11,180 --> 00:30:12,380
but now,

675
00:30:12,860 --> 00:30:14,660
you're visiting a brothel.

676
00:30:15,260 --> 00:30:16,660
I guess you didn't fancy that girl

677
00:30:16,860 --> 00:30:17,780
very much.

678
00:30:17,980 --> 00:30:18,900
That's not true.

679
00:30:19,100 --> 00:30:20,500
It was Second Senior Lei
who brought me there.

680
00:30:20,740 --> 00:30:21,500
Besides, before I got there,

681
00:30:21,500 --> 00:30:22,060
I didn't even know

682
00:30:22,100 --> 00:30:22,820
what kind of place it was.

683
00:30:22,860 --> 00:30:23,820
You didn't know before,

684
00:30:23,820 --> 00:30:24,260
then what about

685
00:30:24,260 --> 00:30:25,340
after you got there?

686
00:30:25,580 --> 00:30:26,700
You do reek of rouge.

687
00:30:27,420 --> 00:30:28,140
You must have spent

688
00:30:28,140 --> 00:30:28,740
quite a while there.

689
00:30:28,740 --> 00:30:29,860
Yes, I did.

690
00:30:30,500 --> 00:30:31,180
But that's because...

691
00:30:31,340 --> 00:30:32,460
Miss Li went there too

692
00:30:32,700 --> 00:30:33,580
and my friend

693
00:30:33,580 --> 00:30:34,580
met a girl there.

694
00:30:34,580 --> 00:30:34,980
And...

695
00:30:37,140 --> 00:30:38,740
I'm not really explaining much here.

696
00:30:39,180 --> 00:30:40,140
So, where's your friend?

697
00:30:43,820 --> 00:30:44,140
Yes,

698
00:30:44,940 --> 00:30:45,940
I went to a brothel,

699
00:30:45,980 --> 00:30:46,620
so what?

700
00:30:46,740 --> 00:30:47,740
Why are you getting mad?

701
00:30:48,220 --> 00:30:49,220
I'm mad?

702
00:30:49,900 --> 00:30:51,100
I'm mad

703
00:30:51,460 --> 00:30:52,860
because I've been practicing
the whole day

704
00:30:52,900 --> 00:30:54,100
while you're having a blast outside.

705
00:30:54,300 --> 00:30:55,620
I feel that this is unfair, okay?

706
00:30:56,340 --> 00:30:57,460
Luoxia, listen to me...

707
00:31:02,380 --> 00:31:03,220
Shameless.

708
00:31:10,260 --> 00:31:11,860
What have I done wrong?

709
00:31:21,780 --> 00:31:22,340
I'm supposed to gather

710
00:31:22,340 --> 00:31:23,460
information about Ye Dingzhi.

711
00:31:24,540 --> 00:31:25,780
Why did I argue

712
00:31:26,340 --> 00:31:27,900
with Baili Dongjun instead

713
00:31:30,180 --> 00:31:31,260
and even slap his face?

714
00:31:33,460 --> 00:31:33,940
Forget it.

715
00:31:35,180 --> 00:31:36,780
I should try to contact Qixuan.

716
00:31:42,380 --> 00:31:43,620
He's coming out!

717
00:31:54,740 --> 00:31:55,980
That's all he can do?

718
00:32:01,780 --> 00:32:02,780
That was fast.

719
00:32:03,620 --> 00:32:05,100
Yeah, is this supposed
to take a long time?

720
00:32:11,340 --> 00:32:11,860
Everyone,

721
00:32:12,180 --> 00:32:13,340
it's not what you think.

722
00:32:13,580 --> 00:32:14,180
Miss Feng and I

723
00:32:14,180 --> 00:32:14,980
were just talking about music.

724
00:32:15,100 --> 00:32:16,020
I didn't do anything to her.

725
00:32:16,060 --> 00:32:16,500
Phooey!

726
00:32:17,500 --> 00:32:18,260
Then what

727
00:32:18,260 --> 00:32:19,460
happened to your hair?

728
00:32:20,460 --> 00:32:21,020
Yeah!

729
00:32:21,180 --> 00:32:22,140
Before this, Miss Feng

730
00:32:22,140 --> 00:32:23,740
had only performed
and never offered other services.

731
00:32:24,300 --> 00:32:25,420
Who do you think you are?

732
00:32:25,580 --> 00:32:25,900
No...

733
00:32:25,940 --> 00:32:27,100
Who are you to do this? How dare you!

734
00:32:27,460 --> 00:32:27,900
Everyone,

735
00:32:28,460 --> 00:32:29,700
my hair came undone because...

736
00:32:29,700 --> 00:32:30,340
That's enough.

737
00:32:30,860 --> 00:32:32,940
Everyone,
stop listening to his nonsense.

738
00:32:33,180 --> 00:32:33,780
Beat him up!

739
00:32:34,180 --> 00:32:34,620
Beat him up!

740
00:32:34,980 --> 00:32:35,860
Wait, everyone!

741
00:32:38,900 --> 00:32:39,340
No,

742
00:32:39,980 --> 00:32:40,620
it's a misunderstanding!

743
00:32:40,620 --> 00:32:41,700
Don't let him get away!

744
00:32:41,700 --> 00:32:42,220
I'm off!

745
00:32:42,860 --> 00:32:43,580
After him!

746
00:32:43,700 --> 00:32:44,540
Beat him up!

747
00:32:57,420 --> 00:32:58,860
Miss Feng, what are you thinking?

748
00:32:59,260 --> 00:32:59,980
You should get some rest.

749
00:33:01,460 --> 00:33:02,060
Linglong,

750
00:33:03,740 --> 00:33:05,340
have I ever told you

751
00:33:06,420 --> 00:33:07,460
about Luoli?

752
00:33:08,380 --> 00:33:10,420
Do you want
to have a heart-to-heart talk, miss?

753
00:33:10,980 --> 00:33:11,860
A heart-to-heart talk?

754
00:33:14,980 --> 00:33:16,020
Maybe I just want

755
00:33:17,260 --> 00:33:18,940
to pour out my feelings.

756
00:33:20,900 --> 00:33:22,660
It's been such a long time.

757
00:33:24,860 --> 00:33:26,300
I'm afraid
that even I might forget everything.

758
00:33:44,580 --> 00:33:46,140
When I was little,

759
00:33:47,100 --> 00:33:48,540
my whole family was exterminated.

760
00:33:49,980 --> 00:33:52,580
My master escaped with me.

761
00:33:53,540 --> 00:33:54,420
Along the way,

762
00:33:55,460 --> 00:33:56,900
he met a kid, who then followed us.

763
00:33:58,660 --> 00:33:59,780
That kid

764
00:34:01,340 --> 00:34:02,580
was Wei Luoli.

765
00:34:04,900 --> 00:34:06,020
Every night,

766
00:34:07,300 --> 00:34:09,180
he would pluck a leaf

767
00:34:10,140 --> 00:34:12,940
and gaze at the moon under the eaves,

768
00:34:13,860 --> 00:34:15,420
playing The Jiangnan Moon.

769
00:34:19,740 --> 00:34:20,500
Whenever

770
00:34:21,580 --> 00:34:23,420
he played the score,

771
00:34:24,780 --> 00:34:25,660
I knew

772
00:34:27,700 --> 00:34:28,900
he was missing home too.

773
00:34:29,700 --> 00:34:30,700
What happened next?

774
00:34:32,060 --> 00:34:33,420
One day, my master

775
00:34:34,740 --> 00:34:36,540
went out with him,
together with his sword.

776
00:34:38,180 --> 00:34:39,540
They never came back.

777
00:34:40,660 --> 00:34:41,540
They said

778
00:34:42,460 --> 00:34:46,180
my master and Luoli were dead.

779
00:34:47,740 --> 00:34:48,700
Miss.

780
00:34:57,460 --> 00:34:58,620
That's the end of the story.

781
00:34:58,860 --> 00:34:59,740
Time to get some rest.

782
00:35:01,460 --> 00:35:01,980
You may leave now.

783
00:35:23,340 --> 00:35:24,660
What's your name?

784
00:35:26,340 --> 00:35:27,100
Wei Luoli.

785
00:35:28,580 --> 00:35:29,980
Where's your family?

786
00:35:32,260 --> 00:35:33,220
They're all dead.

787
00:35:34,340 --> 00:35:35,220
Luoli,

788
00:35:35,660 --> 00:35:37,460
let's be family from now on.

789
00:36:15,100 --> 00:36:16,100
A showdown?

790
00:36:17,980 --> 00:36:19,580
Yes, Your Majesty.

791
00:36:21,500 --> 00:36:24,060
Baili Dongjun is challenging
Master Xie to a liquor showdown

792
00:36:24,100 --> 00:36:25,900
in order to take

793
00:36:25,900 --> 00:36:26,940
the 12-year-old Qiulubai.

794
00:36:27,140 --> 00:36:28,700
Everyone in Tianqi knows about it now.

795
00:36:29,380 --> 00:36:30,700
The Qiulubai

796
00:36:30,900 --> 00:36:32,220
was made in the third year

797
00:36:32,220 --> 00:36:33,500
of your reign.

798
00:36:34,180 --> 00:36:37,300
When it was completed,

799
00:36:37,660 --> 00:36:38,660
you said that if no one

800
00:36:38,660 --> 00:36:40,620
could take it in the next 12 years,

801
00:36:40,820 --> 00:36:42,260
you would use it

802
00:36:42,260 --> 00:36:43,220
as an offering for the gods

803
00:36:43,500 --> 00:36:44,580
during the harvest season.

804
00:36:45,100 --> 00:36:48,380
Now that the 12 years are almost up,

805
00:36:48,580 --> 00:36:51,860
Baili Dongjun is literally...

806
00:36:54,060 --> 00:36:56,900
insulting you publicly.

807
00:37:30,740 --> 00:37:32,980
Your Majesty, the chancellor is here.

808
00:37:37,070 --> 00:37:44,660
[A sigh, and a storm brews]

809
00:37:44,660 --> 00:37:45,860
Nice calligraphy.

810
00:37:46,420 --> 00:37:47,300
Interesting.

811
00:37:48,140 --> 00:37:48,940
As for the couplet,

812
00:37:50,700 --> 00:37:52,060
it's just too pretentious.

813
00:37:53,860 --> 00:37:54,660
Years ago,

814
00:37:55,460 --> 00:37:57,300
when you presented this couplet to me,

815
00:37:57,460 --> 00:37:58,780
I raved about it for a long time.

816
00:37:59,500 --> 00:38:00,380
But now,

817
00:38:00,660 --> 00:38:02,580
even you seem to dislike it.

818
00:38:04,980 --> 00:38:05,660
People

819
00:38:06,540 --> 00:38:08,780
always despise

820
00:38:09,900 --> 00:38:11,140
their own past.

821
00:38:13,820 --> 00:38:14,740
Greetings, Your Majesty.

822
00:38:15,180 --> 00:38:15,900
Offer a seat to him.

823
00:38:16,740 --> 00:38:17,220
Yes, Your Majesty.

824
00:38:29,460 --> 00:38:31,500
Mr. Li, have some tea.

825
00:38:32,780 --> 00:38:33,660
This tea

826
00:38:33,660 --> 00:38:35,460
is a Nanjue specialty
known as Phoenix Snowflakes.

827
00:38:35,780 --> 00:38:36,700
It's hard to come by.

828
00:38:37,380 --> 00:38:37,980
Try it.

829
00:38:41,420 --> 00:38:42,580
Your Majesty, why have you

830
00:38:42,580 --> 00:38:43,380
summoned me today?

831
00:38:48,420 --> 00:38:50,820
When I was young,
I was into poetry and books

832
00:38:51,660 --> 00:38:52,580
instead of martial arts.

833
00:38:53,380 --> 00:38:54,660
My mother was not favored either.

834
00:38:55,340 --> 00:38:56,180
They all thought

835
00:38:56,180 --> 00:38:57,580
I was the most unpromising one
among all the princes.

836
00:38:58,060 --> 00:38:59,700
Luckily, I had two close friends.

837
00:39:00,700 --> 00:39:02,300
One was of the Ye Family from Yunxi,

838
00:39:02,660 --> 00:39:04,460
and the other was
of the Baili Family from Xilin.

839
00:39:05,060 --> 00:39:06,860
Both of them were exceptional warriors.

840
00:39:07,820 --> 00:39:09,260
With their help,

841
00:39:09,500 --> 00:39:10,500
I managed to survive

842
00:39:11,260 --> 00:39:13,140
and ascend the throne.

843
00:39:14,900 --> 00:39:15,660
Later...

844
00:39:17,580 --> 00:39:18,660
I made a terrible mistake,

845
00:39:20,780 --> 00:39:22,180
which still fills me

846
00:39:22,500 --> 00:39:24,100
with much regret.

847
00:39:26,780 --> 00:39:28,140
I received some news earlier,

848
00:39:28,140 --> 00:39:29,340
so I summoned you here

849
00:39:30,300 --> 00:39:32,020
to thank you in person.

850
00:39:32,780 --> 00:39:33,740
That means

851
00:39:34,340 --> 00:39:36,340
you're thanking me

852
00:39:36,740 --> 00:39:37,940
for saving Ye Dingzhi?

853
00:39:38,340 --> 00:39:39,100
Exactly.

854
00:39:40,100 --> 00:39:41,420
Since you have realized your mistake,

855
00:39:41,740 --> 00:39:42,820
why don't you reopen his case?

856
00:39:45,900 --> 00:39:46,700
Forget it.

857
00:39:47,420 --> 00:39:48,500
It's all about your dignity again.

858
00:39:49,460 --> 00:39:49,980
Alright,

859
00:39:50,380 --> 00:39:52,020
I've received your gratitude.

860
00:39:52,860 --> 00:39:53,580
That's all, then.

861
00:39:54,220 --> 00:39:54,860
I'm off.

862
00:39:55,140 --> 00:39:55,820
Wait.

863
00:39:56,500 --> 00:39:57,660
I summoned you here

864
00:39:57,660 --> 00:39:58,700
for another reason.

865
00:40:00,460 --> 00:40:02,020
I heard that you recently

866
00:40:02,140 --> 00:40:03,900
took in a new apprentice

867
00:40:04,580 --> 00:40:05,540
surnamed Baili.

868
00:40:07,780 --> 00:40:09,300
Baili Dongjun.

869
00:40:10,020 --> 00:40:11,100
That is

870
00:40:11,460 --> 00:40:12,820
the grandson of Baili Luochen,

871
